{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d61cf7bb3e","title":"给达赖喇嘛的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3514fc67ca","index":0,"year":1956,"month":8,"day":18,"articleId":"d61cf7bb3e"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[{"id":"3305121cf2","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"d61cf7bb3e","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"达赖喇嘛，即达赖喇嘛·丹增嘉措，西藏宗教领袖之一，当时任全国人大常委会副委员长，西藏自治区筹备委员会主任委员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"6a0481fa7f","type":"title","text":"给达赖喇嘛的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"d61cf7bb3e"},{"id":"3305121cf2","type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的达赖喇嘛","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"d61cf7bb3e"},{"id":"662b40a215","type":"paragraph","text":"给我的两封信都收到了，很高兴","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"d61cf7bb3e"},{"id":"2c0aef58ed","type":"paragraph","text":"西藏自治区筹备委员会已经成立，得到各族人民的拥护，大家满意。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"d61cf7bb3e"},{"id":"e50cc94d2f","type":"paragraph","text":"西藏社会改革问题，听说已经谈开了，很好。现在还不是实行改革的时候，大家谈一谈，先作充分的精神上的准备，等到大家想通了，各方面都安排好了，然后再做，可以少出乱子，最好是不出乱子。四川方面出了一些乱子，主要是亲帝国主义分子和国民党残余分子在那里爆动，我们的工作也有缺点。我希望西藏方面尽量避免出乱子。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"d61cf7bb3e"},{"id":"d6b3d17018","type":"paragraph","text":"陈毅副总理回来，转达了你的意见。我们大家对你很了解，相信你能把西藏的工作做好。我总是担心，汉人在那里和你们合作得不好，得不到藏人的信任。请你负起责来，对于犯了错误的汉人给他们以严格的教育，把他们当作你自己的干部看待。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"d61cf7bb3e"},{"id":"7e1a83a1cf","type":"paragraph","text":"望你保重身体。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"d61cf7bb3e"},{"id":"3531acf946","type":"paragraph","text":"有事随时给我写信。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"d61cf7bb3e"},{"id":"82374c3533","type":"paragraph","text":"这封信你能看懂否？草字尚多，一时改不过来，但比上次少了","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"d61cf7bb3e"},{"id":"51ef97e5d6","type":"subtitle","text":"一点。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"d61cf7bb3e"},{"id":"4e21632cc5","type":"paragraph","text":"遇到困难，务宜忍耐。困难总可以慢慢克服的。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"d61cf7bb3e"},{"id":"aa61c32d0f","type":"paragraph","text":"希望同你见面。","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"d61cf7bb3e"},{"id":"de254b8547","type":"paragraph","text":"祝你健康！","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"d61cf7bb3e"},{"id":"697812f2e0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"d61cf7bb3e"},{"id":"13a492c7f0","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五六年八月十八日","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"d61cf7bb3e"}],"page":{"id":"79d06009b0","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"d61cf7bb3e","start":451,"end":452}}}},"__N_SSG":true}